"title": "8304: loyalty",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8304: loyalty",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A commitment to an ongoing relationship and to the attitude and behaviour demanded by it. It is evident in human relationships and also in the covenant relationship between God and his people.</p>\n<h2>God's loyalty to his people</h2>\n<h3>God's covenant loyalty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:23\">1KI 8:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:14\">2CH 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:5\">NEH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:10\">PSA 25:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:28\">PSA 89:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:17-Ps103:18\">PSA 103:17–103:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:45\">PSA 106:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:3\">ISA 55:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's faithfulness to his promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:14-Ps91:16\">PSA 91:14–91:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>Loyalty to God</h2>\n<h3>The loyalty of God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:18\">1CH 29:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:2\">JER 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:61\">1KI 8:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:32\">2CH 32:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:26\">2CH 35:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:6\">2CH 17:6</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of those loyal to God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:7\">NUM 12:7</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:24\">NUM 14:24</a> <em>Caleb</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14-Josh24:15\">JOS 24:14–24:15</a> <em>Joshua and his family</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:11\">JOB 23:11</a> <em>Job</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:3\">ISA 38:3</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:19\">ACT 4:19</a> <em>Peter and John</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a> <em>Paul</em></p>\n<h3>Failure to show loyalty to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:4\">HOS 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:8\">PSA 78:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:37\">PSA 78:37</a></p>\n<h3>Divided loyalties</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:33\">2KI 17:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:21\">1CO 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:8\">JAS 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Loyalty in human relationships</h2>\n<h3>Loyalty and covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:8\">1SA 20:8</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The loyalty of friends</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:42\">1SA 20:42</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:17\">PRO 17:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:17\">2SA 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:10\">PRO 27:10</a></p>\n<h3>Loyalty within the family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16-Ruth1:17\">RUT 1:16–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:13\">GEN 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:8\">GEN 38:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:29\">GEN 47:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:5\">DEU 25:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:9\">RUT 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:3\">1CO 7:3</a></p>\n<h3>Loyalty to those in authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:26\">EZR 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:2\">ECC 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:27\">MAT 17:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:21\">MAT 22:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1\">TIT 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of loyalty to rulers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:21\">2SA 15:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:14\">1SA 22:14</a> <em>David's loyalty to Saul</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:8\">2SA 3:8</a> <em>Abner's loyalty to Saul's family</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:20\">1KI 12:20</a> <em>the loyalty of Judah to David's house</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:33\">1CH 12:33</a> <em>the men of Zebulun's loyalty to David</em></p>\n<h2>The loyalty of believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:10\">ROM 12:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:3\">PHP 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:17\">1CO 4:17</a> <em>Timothy</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:15-1Cor16:16\">1CO 16:15–16:16</a> <em>the household of Stephanas</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:7\">COL 1:7</a> <em>Epaphras</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:7\">COL 4:7</a> <em>Tychicus</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:9\">COL 4:9</a> <em>Onesimus</em></p>",
